    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Material comprising the seed of a plant, which is the nutrient material for development after germination that is enclosed in a protective coat. Seeds may be processed in various ways for use as materials, or they may be used whole as elements in a design.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
